Bluetooth causes video interference at the hardware level and OS level and there is nothing an app can do to stop this.

replyContent:
If RTH constantly fails this has nothing to do with the phone or the app.  The cause is your Tello's VPS failing to provide correct position data. The App can't fix a broken VPS.
Typical reasons for VPS failure: Dirt in the camera pinhole, scratches on the lens, vibrations from worn props or bent motor shafts.

replyContent: This problem is caused by T1d, not the app. Same problem with original Ryze app.  Video data packets lost due to interference are lost, and no app can bring them back. Use onscreen controllers, or a wired controller: T1S, PS3/4 / XBox gamepad... Also a $5 wifi extender like Xiaomi wifi 2 helps reduce the problem.
